<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE LORD IS COMING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa chuh hung vak ding ahi,
 Kisazo san umun;
 A van In hawih apat hung ding,
 Kisazo san um un;
 I diknau Lalpa chuh ahi,
 A telte vangpie din A hung;
 A pa chutphah ah phuong ina,
 Kisazo san um un.

[V2]
 Na kisazo dem, Moneipa hung tieng (2)
 Na thaumei a vak na dem?
 Zing, sun, zan himahlele?
 Na kisazo dem Moneipa hung tieng?

[V3]
 2. Leiah hungkit pai ding ahi,
 Kisazo sa'n um un;
 Khawvel vai hun hawm pai ina,
 Kisazo sa'n um un;
 Van mi'n Hallelujah tin au,
 Isun tatna a hun ken tieng;
 Lalpen tuok di'n thaumei guongun,
 Kisazo sa'n um un.

[V4]
 3. Ngaiin, mitin di'n hung ina,
 Kisazo sa'n um un;
 Pengkun sapna zapai taitiu,
 Kisazo sa'n um un;
 A thupiekin Vaihawmna ah;
 Gamtin, muntin, mi sam intin,
 Chutphah ma ah dingvek hitiu,
 Kisazo sa'n um un.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>139</hymn_number>
</song>